  • Classes in eu.smartdatalake.simsearch.manager used by eu.smartdatalake.simsearch 
    Class and Description
    AttributeInfo
    Auxiliary class that provides information about the attribute data sources (each named with their queryable column) available for similarity search operations.
    DataIngestor
    Ingests the values of an attribute from a dataset according to user's configuration.
    DatasetIdentifier
    Provides identification for the data regarding a specific attribute available from a data source.
    DataSource
    Instantiates a connection to retrieve attribute values from one of the following possible data sources: (i) a path to a CSV file; or (ii) a JDBC connection pool; or (iii) an HTTP connection to a REST API.
